nder their gaze the same way? Maybe I'm missing something. Probably I'm missing something. And I'm not making myself nearly as clear as I wish I could (my head's a mess so far this year, to be honest). But it sure is fun and pleasing to the eye (if not quite as beautiful, accomplished, and watchable as The Love Witch - this one kind of captures the 70s tone too much?). Some of the music's gorgeous too (even if I was smart enough to realise it wasn't all original this time‚Ä¶ the songs, again, are awful, however‚Ä¶ but I think most of them were meant to be‚Ä¶)
